<% provide(:title, "About") %>
<h1>About</h1>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-6">
        <p>
            Would you like prayer for something? Know a family in financial need? Want a hand
            with home repairs? Have time or skills to donate?
        </p>
        <p>
            You've heard of <strong>crowdfunding</strong> sites like Kickstarter or GoFundMe.
        </p>
        <p>
            Lovefund.us is the very first <strong>lovefunding</strong> site!
        </p>
        <p>
            The goal? To pray for and <strong>fund</strong> needs, with God's
            <strong>love</strong> through <strong>us</strong>, His church.
        </p>
        <p>
            Lovefund.us is an online portal for sharing prayer requests, and financial or
            service needs, for ourselves and others.
        </p>
        <p>
            It is also the place to fund these needs by donating our time, prayer, money,
            expertise... <strong>love.</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">At lovefund.us you can</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <ul>
                <li>Request prayer for yourself and others.</li>
                <li>Fund requests by committing to pray</li>
                <li>Post financial needs for yourself or others</li>
                <li>Safely fund financial needs via the church</li>
                <li>Request help withhousehold projects, and post other needs for yourself or others</li>
                <li>Fund service requests and make your own offers of help and prayer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10">
       <p>
          This web app was created by <a href="https://www.churchindrive.com/">The Church in Drive</a> and <a href="http://fruitful.software">Beau Carnes</a>.
        </p>
        <p><small><i>Disclaimer:</i> Lovefund.us is intended to help match people who want to help others with people who could use the help.  This site is not vetted.  The Church in Drive does not have the resources to verify every post.  Use at your own risk.  Please meet in public places and do not give out personal information until you are comfortable doing so and confident that it is safe.</small></p>
         
    </div>
</div>

